#: ../../chapter-14.rst:155
msgid ""
"These are just minimal examples for showing how ``grid`` works internally. "
"Normally you should start from a copy of the standard ``_scaffold`` app, with "
"all the Session and Authentication stuff already defined. Also, you should "
"follow the standard rules for code, like placing the db definition inside "
"models.py and so on. Using standards will make your code simpler, safer and "
"more maintainable."
