msgstr ""
"post_action_buttons: elenco delle istanze di action_button da includere dopo i "
"pulsanti di azione standard"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:239
msgid ""
"auto_process: Boolean - whether or not the grid should be processed "
"immediately. If False, developer must call grid.process() once all params are "
"setup"
